# Employee Lifecycle Management System

## Objective
To manage employees, attendance, leave, and performance.

## Data Model
- Employee (Main Object)
- Attendance (Child)
- Leave Request
- Performance Review

## Automation
- Leave Approval Flow
- Attendance Auto Marking
- Status Update Flow

## Security
- Role hierarchy
- Profile-based access

## Reports
- Attendance report
- Leave summary
- Employee dashboard

## Key Learnings
- Flow automation
- Data modeling
- Admin-level UI design
